org.opengis.cite.validation

Class SchematronValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opengis.cite.validation.SchematronValidator

  • public class SchematronValidator
extends Object
    Verifies that the content of an XML resource satisfies the constraints defined in an ISO Schematron (ISO 19757-3) schema. The results are presented in an SVRL report. The schema may incorporate abstract patterns and inclusions (sch:include and xi:include elements).
    See Also:
    ISO 19757-3:2006

        public SchematronValidator(Source schema,
                   String phase)
                    throws Exception
        Construct a validator for the given Schematron schema and phase (pattern set).
        Parameters:
        schema - The ISO Schematron schema to use for validation.
        phase - The active phase (rule subset). If null the default phase is used.
        Throws:
        Exception - If any error occurs while attempting to read or preprocess the schema.
